# Enterprise Backend Blueprint

## Introduction

Enterprise Backend Blueprint is a modern Java backend scaffold based on Spring Boot 3.

It aims to provide a production-ready architecture for enterprise applications.

---

## Features

- Spring Boot 3
- JWT Authentication
- Global Exception Handler
- Unified Response
- AOP Logging
- Redis Cache
- Docker Deployment
- API Documentation

---

## Roadmap

- [ ] User Module
- [ ] Role Module
- [ ] Permission Module
- [ ] File Service
- [ ] Scheduled Tasks

---

## Tech Stack

- Java 17
- Spring Boot
- MyBatis
- Redis
- PostgreSQL
